=== TEMPLATES ===

Each template is Markdown with YAML front matter and body sections. One
screen each.

incident-record.md (full cyber incidents)
  Front matter: incident_id, opened_at, severity, status, owner,
    classification
  Body: Summary, Timeline (append-only), Decisions Made, Open Questions,
