## Daily use — short prompts

**Start of day:**
```
Start of day. Read context/ and logs/session-log.md (last 3 entries).
Summarize what's open across current/. Then ask: QUICK or SUSTAINED?
```

**Triage a file from inbox:**
```
Triage inbox/<filename>. Help me classify: which work type, new case or
existing, and what template applies. Propose a case folder name.
```

**Open a new case:**
```
Opening a [cyber-incident | third-party-incident | client-incident |
cyber-event | task]. Brief descriptor: [short name]. Create the folder
with the correct inner structure. Ask me the questions you need to
populate the record's front matter.
```

**Escalate a cyber-event to an incident:**
```
The event at current/cyber-events/<folder> has escalated. Move it to
current/cyber-incidents/ with an appropriate new descriptor. Preserve
the full pre-escalation record. Update the record type and front matter.
```

**Finalize a draft:**
```
The draft at <path> is final and I'm sending it now. Copy to the case's
outputs/ with today's date, copy to archive/summaries/ (or archive/audit/)
if it's that type, remove the draft, and log the send.
```

